videos.description: KeVaughn Allen makes a steal and looks up the court to Egor Koulechov for the throwdown.
videos.headline: Allen heaves it upcourt for Koulechov slam

videos.description: Keith Stone drains a 3 and Kevarrius Hayes draws a foul while battling for the board.
videos.headline: Florida bangs 3, draws foul on same play
